In our testbed, the measurement stations (MSs) are devices that use the IEEE 802.11 protocol (i.e., WiFi) and their wireless cards are set into monitor mode. We performed practical measurements by using an IEEE 802.11 testbed. 


We have generated Received Signal Strength (RSS) values as inputs to our localization algorithm. 
